{"textPanel":{"list":[{"title":"目的","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">通过锌铜原电池的宏观实验现象，从电子的来源、电子的移动方向、溶液内部离子移动方向等微观角度对原电池进行系统分析。</span></p>"},{"title":"原理","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">负极：Zn-2e<sup>-</sup>=Zn<sup>2+</sup></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">正极：Cu<sup>2+</sup>+2e<sup>-</sup>=Cu</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">总反应：Zn+Cu<sup>2+</sup>=Zn<sup>2+</sup>+Cu</span></p>"},{"title":"用品","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">仪器：大烧杯*2、导线*3、开关、电流计、盐桥</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">药品：锌片、铜片、硫酸锌溶液、硫酸铜溶液</span></p>"},{"title":"步骤","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">将置有锌片的ZnSO<sub>4</sub>溶液和置有铜片的CuSO<sub>4</sub>溶液用一个盐桥连接起来，然后将锌片和铜片用导线连接，并在中间串联一个电流表，观察现象。取出盐桥，观察电流计指针的变化情况。</span></p>"},{"title":"现象","data":"<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">接通电路时，电流计指针发生偏转。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:28px\">取出盐桥后，电流计指针回到零点。</span></p>"}],"x":0,"y":0,"width":600,"height":600},"chemData":{"id":"","dataVersion":2,"moduleType":21,"moduleData":{"viewPort":{"x":506.13642497828164,"y":408.8169287905235,"scaleX":1,"scaleY":1},"configData":{"backgroundColor":3422529,"equTypeIsArrow":false,"scientific":false,"equDefaultStatus":true},"moduleConfigData":{"showElectrons":true},"eqs":[{"dataId":"Galvanometer","className":"Galvanometer","UID":16,"x":816.6729303891746,"y":-15.852974110551173,"rotation":0,"insIdx":1,"attrMode":0},{"dataId":"SaltBridge","className":"SaltBridge","UID":8,"x":1995.9863886707672,"y":545.7163372413173,"rotation":0,"insIdx":1,"attrMode":0,"type":0},{"dataId":"HugeBeaker","className":"HugeBeaker","UID":7,"x":1318.508407910665,"y":614.8742643401856,"rotation":0,"insIdx":2,"chemicalData":{"phases":[{"phaseType":"g","temperature":300,"chemicals":[{"formula":"O2","valence":0,"mol":0.01065980274236228},{"formula":"N2","valence":0,"mol":0.04263921096944912}]}]},"showEleAni":true},{"dataId":"HugeBeaker","className":"HugeBeaker","UID":6,"x":808.508407910665,"y":614.8742643401856,"rotation":0,"ins